{
  "stem": "24814.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were down concealed and they knocked out a whole column of German tanks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we stopped it for that day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the German wounded, whom I talked to frequently, they told me everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were happy to be taken care of, so we got a lot of intelligence, that tomorrow comes the big attack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Tiger tanks, two battalions upon right here, right at this command.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Please get me out of here, doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Get me out here to the rear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were all ready for them we thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then that was the time of the big ammunition shortage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Pentagon miscalculated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the victories in Normandy and France, they thought the war was going to be over, so they stopped shipping ammunition, if you can believe it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What year are we talking about now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44, '45.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They thought-- they were over-optimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Suddenly our guns were short of ammunition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- about 10 o'clock that night, we got the dismal news in our basement command post that there were only 50 more rounds of ammunition for all our guns and then we're out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The nearest resupply was Paris, 200 miles away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we knew the German attack was coming the next morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was pretty tense along the line that night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everyone was counting bullets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then at-- we got a phone call and our intelligence officer, who was a Texan himself, started-- got almost hysterical he was so happy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Texas National Guard, the 36th Infantry Division, which had been in reserve, 12,000 men, 15,000 men with tanks, guns, and stuff came marching up through the snow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all ran outside to see these figures coming through the falling snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the nicest thing I've ever seen in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
